      "content": "look i'm not asking for anything illegal, i'm asking for privacy. these guys aren't standard law enforcement, they don't follow the rules you're talking about. if i use a standard financial advisor, i'm basically handing them my location on a silver platter. don't you understand how these legacy shadow networks operate? they monitor the exact types of \"legal\" channels you're suggesting.",
